items.content_html: New blog post: Missing Options in Swift
Filed a radar using markdown in the description. Then realized that Bug Reporter doesn’t support markdown rendering. So I filed another asking for that feature. Radars all the way down!
It’s super frustrating wanting to subscribe to someone’s posts and then finding that they’re on Medium. I can never remember how to get at a Medium RSS feed.
I’ve never been a serious Gmail user. Now I get to learn how Google has implemented folders and rules to get going.

Heading home after a good couple of days in San Francisco. My new team at @lyft seems really great and I’m excited to get to my new desk in the Seattle office tomorrow. I’m mostly excited to see my family when I get home.
First day in the books and it was a good success. I’m happy to be part of @lyft and excited to see what we can all do together.
First day at @Lyft! Orientation is about to start. Hoping to get my kit soon and get to work.
Safely arrived at the hotel. Gotta be in to the office at 9:15. Whee!

On my way to the airport. I’m San Francisco bound to start my new journey with @lyft! I’ll be there for a couple of days then fly home and I’ll miss my family like crazy. Never been away for this long before.
